    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a flawless mechanical pedigree, including a documented VANOS overhaul and factory-spec rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis dynamics remain razor-sharp with original bushings and perfectly preserved damping. Every individual throttle body is calibrated to factory tolerances, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and that signature metallic rasp up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Finished in original paint with zero orange peel or oxidation, this is a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
