    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the black leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing no signs of bolster wear, fading, or aging. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with full documentation and both keys included. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key enthusiast car that has been pampered since day one. No stories, no excuses\u2014just absolute perfection for the discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
