      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single blemish to be found\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine condition! If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
