      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, ensuring structural rigidity and mechanical precision. The factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock and MacPherson strut front/multi-link rear suspension remain in peak operating condition. With zero deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage, this chassis delivers a pure, analog driving experience that meets the highest collector standards.",
